  Source:
    Title: Kulârnava Tantra
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=The Extraction of Poison with Poison
---
Shiva, the Terrible God, has taught in the doctrine of the left hand that
spiritual progress is only possible with the aid of the very things which
are the cause of man’s fall.
